channel.title: Greeny is House?
channel.description:
So over the past 3 days I've been away, I thought I'd reflect on a few experiences and discoveries I had for lulz.
I have basically spent a couple of days at Oxford (University). On this trip I did not only make discoveries about myself but also about other people, mainly, how much a bunch of twats southerners are.
Oxford is obviously one of the most well known and prestigious universities in the world, it's a beautiful city but fuck me is it full of fuckers.
1st day, I turn up in a huddy and jeans, all these posh faggot toffs are walking around with their parents in suits. FOR FUCK SAKE it's the university supposed to be making an impression on US not US on THEM. So these people where strutting around looking at me like dirt - so I spent both days walking into them lulz.
Other thing was, I was with 2 friends, now these guys are just some guys from Maths, they aren't within my close friends group and don't really know an awful lot about me. They were kind of shocked at the racist and elitist comments I made all the time but also focused in on the negativity I convey all the time.
I apparently: -Always moan -Always miserable -Always insult others -Hate to lose
Mixed with the fact I'm looking to study Medicine they concluded I am Gregory House and now call me House all the time.
So should Greeny be renamed to House? Am I like House? ...personally I love the TV series and idolise him just wondering if anyone else noticed these traits in me.
Just to finish off a little something that me laugh which I found:
[img]http://img399.imageshack.us/img399/433/dsc00128wr6.jpg[/img]
[i]Sorry for this absurd, pointless topic but I'm deeply bored...[/i]
